Who is driving the surge in 3-point attempts?

Three teams—Seattle Storm, Phoenix Mercury, and Washington Mystics—are leading the way, stretching defenses with multiple 3-point

shooters. In 2018, all three teams attempted 3-pointers at nearly the same pace as the 2017-2018 NBA league average.
